controller

Class PaparazziProblemController

  • java.lang.Object
    • controller.PaparazziProblemController

  • public class PaparazziProblemController
extends java.lang.Object
    Paparazzi problem controller to manage different data set runs. Controller holds and manages an PaparazziProblemModel. Controller is implemented in a Singleton pattern.
